couple things about me and my fleet :) 

1. Customer Service & Customer Safety are my main priorities and the rest follow behind.

2. I'm a very responsible & easy going host.. proudly a 5-star host.. my cars are very well-maintened, super reliable, great gas mileage, and super clean.

A few minor instructions and clarifications: 

1. from the minute a customer picks up the car, the customer can return the car within a 2 hour period and will process a full refund if for some reason the car does not meet the customer standards. 

2. if you are picking up / dropping off the car at my location then the entire process will be contactless.. full instructions will be sent out to you once you book the car.

3. we do offer an airport delivery option: we will meet you at the terminal outside and hand you the keys and at the drop-off time, we will meet you at the terminal outside to get the keys from you.

4. Highly recommend adding the post-cleaning option and we will take care of the cleaning for you otherwise please return the car as picked up to avoid cleaning fees. 

5. Highly recommend adding the prepaid re-fuel option and we will take care of the re-fueling otherwise please return the car as picked up to avoid gas fees. 

6. you can always extend your trip if you need to do so.. please contact me prior to your original drop-off time, you have to extend before that to avoid any delay fees. 

7. I try to keep the reservations locally so I can better serve my customers if needed.  

8. Car usually comes with at least a 1/4 tank gas. You are asked to return it with the same gas level

"The only way for me to improve is your feedbacks.."
